data.description: Great starter home located near Interstate I-81. Close to Pennsylvania line. Bright living room. Upper level has oversize primary bedroom w/ balcony! Full upper level hall bathroom and 2 bedrooms. 2nd and 3rd bedroom is a walk thru. Floored attic space for ample storage. Basement w/ inside & outside entrance, great for workshop or additional storage! Off street parking. Local park within walking distance.
